{"tid":1582290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[策略建議] 火燒後欄的方向--豬肉、習近平","createTime":"2019-09-20T03:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T16:05:14.000Z","uid":44646,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba78c53cd33ab796363d7e514b06c2e71e2eeaff","tid":1582290,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:46:27.000Z","msg":"火燒後欄的建議：<br />\n<br />\n‧10.1唔好燒五星旗，改燒黨旗<br />\n理由：好多中國人視國旗為神聖，我地無咩必要樹敵太多<br />\n<br />\n‧現階段輸出革命，可以針對習近平來打<br />\n中國人現時最關心咩事？<br />\n豬肉價格飛升。<br />\n點解豬肉貴？因為習近平<br />\n<br />\n中國本來主要由無豬瘟的美國進口豬肉<br />\n貿易戰一起，習包子為反擊，就減買美國豬<br />\n改買俄國豬；而俄國係非洲豬瘟疫區<br />\n結果順手引入豬瘟，全國本地養豬業受累<br />\n豬肉價飛升<br />\n<br />\n一個ON9仔令全中國人民受苦<br />\n而全國無聲出<br />\n習包子剛修憲，可以無限連任<br />\n在大陸已經無人可以批評佢<br />\n但香港居然幫國出聲，中國人會點諗?<br />\n<br />\n香港人在此時將&rdquo;豬瘟&rdquo;&mdash;&ldquo;豬價飛升&rdquo;連上&rdquo;習包子&rdquo;<br />\n有可能CONNECT埋中國人"},{"pid":"07231df82f30ba31bf6d56448b1c63d8564e119a","tid":1582290,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"非洲豬瘟與貿易戰關係簡介<br />\n<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/63513669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhuanlan.zhihu.com%2Fp%2F63513669&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8n4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=c52456cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/63513669</a>"},{"pid":"3837a9156049f048b06d58bfd4276d6c690c61be","tid":1582290,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"b9d0623b95c475c6af96bd1cbf3a0e6e278b6046","tid":1582290,"uid":57438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"推有用腦post"},{"pid":"91a7b7b3c2a95e8d152a96489fd26b4bbd2d750b","tid":1582290,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:53:19.000Z","msg":"成日諗火燒後欄，<br />\n你要令目標對象有共鳴<br />\n<br />\n全中國都知豬價升同習包子有關<br />\n但唔可以出聲<br />\n香港人幫口指出<br />\n大道理係指出專制之弊<br />\n策略上，你唔燒國旗<br />\n改為向習近平畫像掟雞蛋<br />\n一樣會在外國傳媒瘋傳<br />\n最終出口轉內銷，傳回大陸"},{"pid":"9b40097b4c51a6b655870e260454b5ad70eb9a6b","tid":1582290,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"五星旗燒過幾次啦，<br />\n影像上欠新鮮感<br />\n大大幅習包子畫被掟番茄，未出現過<br />\n<br />\n外國記者問原因<br />\n大道理係反獨裁<br />\n策略上同時幫中國人發聲：係佢令全國食無肉"},{"pid":"457530eddf3c674b75531a06e5e3c787a479bb9a","tid":1582290,"uid":272292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:00:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aaa023eb135b14caabae10cb0e97ba63fee2e2a8","tid":1582290,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REzO1La.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREzO1La.jpg&h=1b62a4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h38Ttqa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh38Ttqa.png&h=f36d1035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b1724c0226cb5fa1399a82861194e8ec19cb2f1","tid":1582290,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡快行動！"},{"pid":"5ffe906e9846d2958f3f423cbcf97d263d4381c3","tid":1582290,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"聽講十一閱兵期間嘅和平遊行，唔會有清場鎮壓！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585568</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}